,-0.014256822,0.05079415,0.02588491,-0.008159659,-0.079526745,-0.059117466,-0.016122187,-0.021026075,-0.014142865,-0.016531793,0.016171228,0.01878148,-0.040111292,0.000500715,-0.023281958,0.018287465,-0.05891305,0.041649885,0.026597843,-0.014368551,-0.00035011,0.029341958,0.020122442,-0.041526187,-0.030424075,0.003001929,0.045145225,0.00630601,-0.049999766,0.03782175,-0.052147634,0.012428995,-0.022920292,-0.026785223,0.011894959,0.011828633,-0.004450784,-0.040928382,-0.04434718,0.018474292,-0.046717774,0.002672986,0.006188248,-0.010241443,-0.041058995,0.046647985,-0.000247215,0.031062942,-0.026824705,0.03285662,-0.001927991,-0.000696683,0.011148749,-0.006359869,-5.6324e-05,-0.03413111,-0.029049972,-0.03388738,-0.030547658,-0.03320607,0.02415013,-0.010615431,0.02326351,-0.00584291,0.037542667,-0.012425749,0.005782819,-0.033676635,0.003951958,-0.020612087,-0.008102174,-0.009722301,0.038520515,0.020940863,0.043233875,-0.016322507]'::vector, '2026-03-14T19:51:56.569Z');
INSERT INTO knowledge_patterns (id, clause_pattern, category, contract_type, risk_level, why_risky, safer_alternative, jurisdiction_notes, embedding, created_at) VALUES ('d4e3f4a5-6b7c-4d8e-bf1a-2b3c4d5e6f7a', 'The arbitration proceedings, including the existence of the arbitration, all documents and materials submitted, all testimony given, and the arbitrator''s award, shall be strictly confidential. Neither party shall disclose any information regarding the arbitration to any third party, except as required by law or to enforce the arbitrator''s award. The Employee agrees that any breach of this confidentiality provision shall result in liquidated damages of fifty thousand dollars ($50,000) payable to the Company.', 'arbitration', '["employment"]'::jsonb, 'red', 'This confidentiality clause hides the very existence of the arbitration and imposes a $50,000 penalty for talking about it. If the company is engaging in widespread discrimination or wage theft, this prevents employees from discovering a pattern of similar claims. It also prevents you from warning others about predatory practices or discussing your experience with journalists or advocacy groups. The steep financial penalty further discourages anyone from speaking up, even when they have every right to do so.', 'The parties agree to maintain reasonable confidentiality regarding the specific details of arbitration proceedings. This confidentiality obligation does not restrict either party from (a) disclosing the existence and general nature of the dispute, (b) communicating with government agencies, legal counsel, or tax advisors, (c) making disclosures protected by the National Labor Relations Act, whistleblower statutes, or anti-discrimination laws, or (d) discussing workplace conditions with other employees or former employees. No liquidated damages shall apply to any disclosure.', 'NLRA section 7 protects employees'' right to discuss terms and conditions of employment, including dispute outcomes. The Defend Trade Secrets Act 18 USC section 1833(b) provides immunity for whistleblower disclosures. NLRB has found that confidentiality provisions in arbitration agreements violate NLRA section 8(a)(1) when they chill protected concerted activity (NLRB General Counsel Memo GC 23-02). UK Employment Rights Act 1996 section 43B whistleblower protections cannot be waived. EU Whistleblower Protection Directive 2019/1937 prohibits contractual restrictions on reporting.', '[0.018853318,-0.006844223,-0.03366314,0.014284441,-0.015505954,-0.020923318,-0.031090917,0.007578245,-0.006463073,0.08100329,-0.025210118,0.02666064,-0.011283943,0.001390767,0.02970596,-0.039579894,0.006598153,5.7104e-05,0.022175698,-0.015975168,-0.021692252,-0.05028912,-0.003920912,0.0368771,0.017505098,-0.004036879,-0.01006155,0.000505411,0.018689098,-0.028837696,0.006143484,0.035596926,0.02434537,-0.01141577,-0.017020162,0.019001016,0.061661083,0.004387775,-0.01460385,-0.015878562,0.005185216,0.020148942,0.041617606,0.047608223,-0.02892843,-0.014069656,0.040545184,0.009459769,-0.004907181,0.04388398,0.004747748,-0.016303577,-0.017646069,0.023887815,0.003248252,-0.014145143,0.045243043,-0.008152185,0.009628079,-0.012191814,0.03349203,-0.04396858,-0.017499631,0.03601389,-0.02654037,-0.032587297,0.000999046,-0.008753973,-0.01205193,-0.005943226,0.050243724,0.06891234,-0.01374461,0.065165065,0.042009007,-0.01145435,0.021163102,0.02254518,0.013251328,0.002600257,-0.05374415,-0.0269525,0.018344466,-0.013272361,-0.040896274,0.002674758,-0.005950731,0.007601225,0.08903075,0.008737361,-0.052749492,-0.021619385,0.060218785,-0.06150715,0.020542977,0.0134487,-0.000853211,0.016846497,0.019221958,0.014958977,-0.050918147,-0.010640128,-0.012170948,0.027870936,0.027633984,0.033645004,-0.04562088,0.004870386,-0.008092906,0.002646952,0.002506884,-0.014651995,-0.041379355,-0.032672673,0.006368972,-0.032689992,-0.009933007,-0.025891453,0.035172325,0.027670955,-0.051427417,-0.041917082,-0.01661654,0.006483576,0.042389013,-0.00