0.008620268,0.003913239,0.039692804,0.024362614,0.015210474,0.005817974,-0.016090952,0.042312764,-0.035901684,-0.014927865,-0.017213333,0.026667127,0.03175372,-0.009855326,0.003424494,-0.021594906,-0.01687256,0.04872577,0.043764435,0.01569207,-0.055918563,-0.03491261,-0.001805313,0.009075103,0.028416015,-0.027752062,0.02325302,-0.04746387,-0.008090257,-0.03429851,-0.03370161,-0.026013028,-0.016914831,-0.05196366,0.04776721,-0.008643203,-0.001093323,-0.011783861,-0.030876212,0.023430282,-0.008735245,0.017925914,-0.013896692,0.0509656,0.06110197,-0.011913043,0.03862642,0.006198266,0.003017212,-0.014899921,-0.014834927,0.028662518,-0.012262985,-0.000366072,0.049025543,-0.073579386,0.022915712,-0.02572332,0.064373344,0.001954255,-0.006672368,-0.035183307,0.010003211,-0.02490318,-0.031895507,0.02609702,-0.04972379,0.011303987,-0.06832419,-0.040218107,0.045526776,-0.056509912,0.001348593]'::vector, '2026-03-14T19:51:56.569Z');
INSERT INTO knowledge_patterns (id, clause_pattern, category, contract_type, risk_level, why_risky, safer_alternative, jurisdiction_notes, embedding, created_at) VALUES ('d4e7f8a9-0b1c-4d2e-bf5a-6b7c8d9e0f1a', 'The Employee shall not, during or after employment, directly or indirectly, make any disparaging or derogatory statements, whether oral, written, or electronic, concerning the Company, its officers, directors, employees, shareholders, products, services, business practices, or financial condition, to any person, entity, media outlet, or on any social media platform, whether publicly or privately.', 'restrictive_covenants', '["employment"]'::jsonb, 'yellow', 'This non-disparagement clause is permanent (lasting forever after you leave) and incredibly broad. It covers private conversations, social media posts, and even truthful statements. You could not leave a negative Glassdoor review, warn a friend about workplace problems, or discuss your experience with a journalist. It also potentially conflicts with your right to report workplace safety violations, discrimination, or other illegal conduct to government agencies -- protections that cannot be waived by contract.', 'During and after employment, both the Company and the Employee agree not to make public statements that are knowingly false and materially damaging about the other party. This clause does not restrict (a) truthful statements made in the course of legal proceedings, regulatory filings, or government investigations, (b) communications protected by the National Labor Relations Act or equivalent legislation, (c) good-faith reports of workplace safety, discrimination, harassment, or other legal violations, or (d) reviews or commentary on employment experience platforms.', 'US National Labor Relations Act section 7 protects employees'' rights to discuss working conditions; overly broad non-disparagement clauses violate NLRA section 8(a)(1) per NLRB General Counsel Memo GC 23-02 (2023). The Defend Trade Secrets Act 18 USC section 1833(b) provides whistleblower immunity. UK Employment Rights Act 1996 section 43B protects whistleblower disclosures. EU Directive 2019/1937 (Whistleblower Protection Directive) prohibits contractual waivers of reporting rights.', '[-0.002981303,0.010454789,-0.001148903,0.002766239,-0.04382835,0.029516533,-0.014838175,0.026194926,-0.010258144,0.035560053,-0.016134594,0.007992836,-0.08179465,-0.078419976,0.03376593,0.02589818,0.030098962,-0.017551852,-0.027684174,0.029001309,-0.021767423,0.029944181,0.013334741,0.012345016,-0.003560781,-0.031225014,-0.025742088,-0.015540632,-0.008851786,-0.00281059,0.011695903,0.018034432,0.006363279,0.006537933,0.004626744,-0.03400267,-0.010384335,-0.05788049,0.04592579,-0.013591776,0.032744225,0.0358009,0.007409554,-0.02397296,0.004871754,0.003451125,0.010926647,0.020340292,-0.020237392,0.011147298,0.065394625,-0.00121259,-0.07015965,-0.028284896,-0.033611145,0.002978711,0.03971757,0.04390176,-0.018245973,0.001494953,0.054438453,-0.030546032,-0.02335847,0.006476679,-0.013162358,-0.040245216,0.013543344,-0.017051456,-0.023882464,-0.001531528,0.07193402,-0.001325494,0.004116194,0.011676626,-0.012441339,-0.000390366,-0.011333684,0.03786331,0.00609037,-0.015606681,-0.064952776,0.005386146,-0.031453095,0.006270731,-0.030133506,0.006541421,-0.007587993,-0.025964575,-0.023606377,0.022007642,-0.012778583,-0.015340126,0.042448435,-0.020552391,-0.01818016,-0.055723052,0.013222191,-0.017312856,-0.040042892,-0.03436202,-0.012789069,-0.014715282,0.0331449,-0.016504657,0.04998671,-0.019599931,-0.04352023,0.016729021,-0.004476232,0.027288035,-0.007912465,-0.003325587,-0.012112383,-0.001929342,0.007776965,0.00677191,-0.01835154,-0.006798276,-0.011380893,-0.039930757,-0.015729534,0.015805375,-0.038674463,0.004635843,-0.013350585,0.03178732,0.02108945,-0.005104235,0.00360013,0.036829896,0.037858445,-0.026777683,-0.026593214,-0.012104562,0.006844389,0.038597774,0.01773894,0.012894114,-0.019574318,0.015285715,-0.00637986,-