0.060790226,-0.061085813,-0.04658548,0.008928341,-0.009002101,-0.061479572,0.034170594,0.07434143,-0.028377054,-0.07131501,0.032344524,0.000229506,-0.034677695,-0.027433472,0.004424432,-0.038433313,-0.015872274,-0.030633094,-0.061137445,-0.03416816,0.03566028,-0.047420464,0.012660245,0.006828182,-0.006409889,-0.070496306,0.012063639,0.044804145,0.000479197,0.006916979,0.018777996,0.023466075,-0.002691323,-0.011226393,0.022225386,-0.026617618,0.024765752,0.008823792,-0.00826907,-0.024632087,-0.064186685,-0.008462989,-0.008936727,0.006731958,0.029464904,-0.012793137,-0.014373048,0.022541957,-0.014602145,-0.015152344,-0.07041562,-0.044741075,0.012440283,0.010667709,-0.02744212,-0.026735175,0.014148357,0.020533083,0.044968523,0.008455256,0.04605035]'::vector, '2026-03-14T19:51:47.730Z');
INSERT INTO knowledge_patterns (id, clause_pattern, category, contract_type, risk_level, why_risky, safer_alternative, jurisdiction_notes, embedding, created_at) VALUES ('d4a3b4c5-6d7e-4f8a-8b1c-2d3e4f5a6b7c', 'The Company reserves the right, at its sole and absolute discretion, to change the Employee''s job title, duties, responsibilities, reporting structure, compensation, benefits, work location, or work schedule at any time without the Employee''s consent and without prior notice. The Employee agrees that no such change shall constitute a breach of this Agreement or give rise to any claim for constructive dismissal or constructive termination.', 'termination', '["employment"]'::jsonb, 'red', 'This clause gives the company unlimited power to change every aspect of your job -- your role, pay, location, and hours -- without your agreement or even advance notice, and then says you cannot claim this amounts to being forced out (known as ''constructive dismissal''). In practice, this could mean you are demoted, relocated across the country, or have your salary cut, and you would have no legal recourse. This attempts to waive a fundamental employment right that most jurisdictions consider non-waivable.', 'The Company may propose reasonable changes to the Employee''s duties, work location, or reporting structure to meet legitimate business needs. Any change to the Employee''s base salary, job title, or primary work location (beyond thirty miles from the current location) shall require the Employee''s prior written consent. If the Employee does not consent to a material change, either party may terminate the employment upon thirty (30) days'' notice, and the Employee shall be entitled to severance as set forth in Section X.', 'UK Employment Rights Act 1996 sections 94-98 protect against unfair dismissal, including constructive dismissal where the employer fundamentally breaches the employment contract. The implied duty of mutual trust and confidence (Malik v BCCI [1998] AC 20) prevents employers from unilaterally making fundamental changes. EU Directive 2019/1152 Article 6 requires written notice of changes to working conditions. Attempting to waive constructive dismissal rights prospectively is unenforceable in the UK (Autoclenz Ltd v Belcher [2011] UKSC 41) and most EU member states.', '[-0.002776477,0.038867332,-0.014341259,-0.00121747,-0.043340534,0.024424786,-0.024799865,-0.00968006,-0.014961299,0.016805086,0.015334539,0.004606951,-0.031005643,-0.013992479,0.005365699,0.04358115,-0.020901969,0.026440173,0.014094779,0.00903461,-0.003889092,0.000447379,-0.0494645,0.011276041,0.03543084,-0.014094943,0.017697254,0.019164072,0.018305471,0.040008165,0.052282184,0.042218644,-0.05259213,0.014180456,0.027539639,-0.024662148,0.044122856,-0.07023989,0.017179882,-0.005640984,0.015194024,0.024534566,0.030455261,0.034228172,0.013886136,-0.002288525,-0.029517598,0.008826544,-0.060681038,-0.004323689,0.0483573,-0.003101139,0.001097336,0.071182154,-0.010259422,-0.011006749,0.03796731,0.07743864,0.014650179,-0.014151229,0.05091816,-0.006566687,-0.021906218,0.015426497,-0.004157866,-0.08917853,-0.01912103,0.001992254,0.005508695,-0.003597053,0.07784296,0.010576206,0.005612433,0.043196145,0.011428013,0.004435588,-0.023190748,0.022306446,-0.01499295,0.024079282,-0.04837505,-0.023126684,0.00041448,0.03670826,-0.03452542,-0.005161184,0.009046893,0.00182234,0.018511174,0.06531529,0.000155182,-0.047797326,0.015172997,0.010349519,0.040542047,-0.004973345,-0.005562078,0.02371561,-0.022321366,-0.018849138,-0.02280939,0.012227791,-0.023527075,-0.010241373,0.03830606,-0.07442707,-0.00047532,-0.019847276,-0.011902626,0.04378586,0.010633026,-0.028563427,0.022929793,0.04920995,0.000304867,-0.023733431,-0.009870734,-0.015756968,0.059912104,0.024954697,0.000208434,-0.008723446,-0.015147982,-0.008108477,-0.018437784,0.010103037,-0.015305509,0.011075256,-0.02242992,-0.026377028,0.033073165,-0.009858829,0.023193525,0.01106886,-0.02363759,0.04224957,0.021259438,0.0